=Description=

"CrowdBnk gathers together people with ideas and people who want to help those ideas roll into reality. It’s a way for thousands of people to help one person get their idea off the ground.

Great ideas have their own velocity. Once an idea is set in motion, people – and money – will crowd around it. Got an idea? Use CrowdBnk to reach out to new supporters. Got some money? Invest in ideas you believe in for as little as £10. Feel the thrill of building something new. An app, a shop, a bar, a beer, that wouldn’t be here if it wasn’t for you.

With great ideas, and people who believe in them, anything’s possible. Between us, we can do it."
(http://www.crowdbnk.com/pages/about)

